<headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 28 at 1:54PM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Showers and Thunderstorms Capable of Gusty Winds and Hail...
Showers and thunderstorms are developing across portions of
Southwest Montana this afternoon. Thunderstorms will be capable of
producing gusty winds in excess of 40 mph and hail of a half inch
in diameter or larger. These thunderstorms will move northeastward
with time. Remember, when thunder roars, go indoors.</description>
